<template>
    <b-navbar>
        <template slot="brand">
              <router-link to="/" class="nav-link"><font-awesome-icon icon="home" /></router-link>
        </template>

        <template slot="end">
            <router-link to="/profile">
                <font-awesome-icon icon="cog" />
              </router-link>
        </template>
    </b-navbar>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  name: "NavBar",
  methods: {
    login() {
      this.$auth.loginWithRedirect();
    },
    logout() {
      this.$auth.logout();
      this.$router.push({ path: "/" });
    }
  }
};
</script>

<style>
#mobileAuthNavBar {
  min-height: 125px;
  justify-content: space-between;
}
</style>
